Package de.tudarmstadt.ukp.lmf.transform.wordnet

Class Summary
LexicalEntryGenerator Instance of this class offers methods for creating LexicalEntry out of WordNet's data
RelatedFormGenerator This class offers methods for generating RelatedForms of LexicalEntries
SenseGenerator This class offers methods for generating instances of Sense class from WordNet 3.0
SenseGeneratorTest Tests methods of SenseGenerator class.
Tests are made for WordNet 3.0 data and UBY-LMF DTD version 0.2.0.
SenseRelationGenerator This class offers methods for generating instances of SenseRelation-class
SubcategorizationFrameExtractor This class extracts subcategorization frames of WordNet 3.0 by parising subcategorization-mapping file.
SynsetGenerator Instance of this class offers methods for creating Synset instances out of WordNet's data
SynsetRelationGenerator This class is used for extraction of synset-relations, defined in Uby-LMF, out of WordNet's data.
TestSuite Runs all tests for wordnet-gpl module: WNConvUtilTest and SenseGeneratorTest.
WNConverter Instance of this class converts WordNet 3.0 to LMF-format
